🟢 Slide 1 – Title

Assalamu Alaikum wa Rahmatullahi wa Barakatuh 🌸
Aaj ka topic hai: “Islamic Perspective se Personality Development”
👉 Main chahungi ke sab log actively participate karein.

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 2 – Objectives

Objectives (Maqasid):

Islami shakhsiyat ke bunyadi oṣaaf ko samajhna
Qur’an o Sunnat ki roshni mein apni islaah aur tarbiyat ki koshish
Nabi Kareem ﷺ ki seerat se rahnumai haasil karna
Amali sargarmiyon ke zariye soch aur amal mein tabdeeli lana

✅ Ham apni shaksiyat ko Islam ki roshni mein samajhne ki koshish karenge.
✅ Qur’an aur Hadith se guidance lenge.
✅ Role models se seekhenge.
👉 Sawal: Aapke hisaab se ek “ideal Muslim personality” kaisi honi chahiye?

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 3 – Icebreaker (Who am I?)

Activity 🎯: Sab apne papers pe likhein –
👉 3 achi aadatein
👉 3 buri aadatein
Phir sochiye: Kya yeh wahi shaksiyat hai jo Allah ko pasand hai?

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 4 – Personality in Islam

Islam kehta hai:
👉 Inner Qualities = iman, sabr, haya, sachai
👉 Outer Behaviour = baat karna, dress, ikhlaq
👉 Sawal: Aapke khayal se “inner qualities” zyada aham hain ya “outer behaviour”?

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 5 – Qur’an & Hadith

📖 Surah Al-Qalam 68:4 – Nabi ﷺ ko “azeem akhlaq” wala kaha gaya.
📖 Surah Hujurat 49:13 – Allah ke nazdeek sabse behtareen wo hai jo sabse mutaqi hai.  //mutaqi= Jo Allah se darne wala ho (Taqwa rakhta ho)
📖 Surah Furqan 25:63 – Rahman ke bande narmi aur tawazu ke sath chalte hain.
📖 Surah Al-Mu’minun 23:1–11 – Mo’min ki qualities.

💡 Hadith: “Best among you wo hai jiska akhlaq best ho.” (Tirmidhi)
👉 Question: Kya aapko lagta hai ke sirf namaz aur ibadat hi personality banati hai?

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 6 – Key Qualities

Islamic Personality ke qualities:
✅ Sachai = honest
✅ Sabr
✅ Haya  //Haya = Sharm, Modesty, Purity of Heart aur Self-respect.
✅ Tawakkul  =trust
✅ Adl = inasf
✅ Maaf karna
👉 Activity: Sab apne liye ek quality choose karein jo abhi sabse zyada improve karni hai.

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 7–8 – Role Models

👉 Nabi ﷺ – Mercy (Rehmat), Honesty (Sachai), Humility (Tawazu‘-Ghamand na karna, logon ke saath narmi aur izzat se rehna.)
👉 Hazrat Ayesha (RA) – Intelligence, knowledge, courage-Himmat
👉 Hazrat Fatima (RA) – Simplicity, modesty, piety-Taqwa
👉 Question: Aap in mein se kisko apna role model banana pasand karengi, aur kyu?

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🟢 Slide 9 – Activity (What would the Prophet do?)

Scenarios:

1️⃣ Hijab par mazaaq banaya jaye

👉 Agar koi hijab ka mazaaq banaye, toh:
✅ Main shanti aur izzat ke sath reply karungi.
✅ Gussa ya react nahi karungi, kyunki haya aur hijab Allah ke liye hai.
📖 Qur’an: “Rahman ke bande narmi se jawab dete hain.” (Surah Furqan 25:63)
🌸 Nabi ﷺ bhi narmi aur hikmat ke sath jawab dete.

2️⃣ Galat ilzam lag jaye

👉 Agar mujh par jhoota ilzam lag jaye:
✅ Main sabr aur dua karungi, kyunki Allah hi insaf karne wala hai.
✅ Sachai par qaim rahungi.
📖 Qur’an: “Inna Allaha yudafi‘u ‘anilladhina amanu” — Allah mo’minon ki himayat karta hai. (Surah Hajj 22:38)
🌸 Nabi ﷺ par bhi ilzam lagaye gaye, lekin unhone sabr kiya aur Allah se madad maangi.

3️⃣ Dosti mein jealousy ho

👉 Agar mujhe apni dost se jealousy ho:
✅ Main apne dil ko saaf karne ki koshish karungi.
✅ Uske liye dua karungi, kyunki jealousy dil ko sakht karti hai.
📖 Qur’an: “Aur hasad se bacho jab woh hasad kare.” (Surah Falaq 113:5)
🌸 Nabi ﷺ ne hamesha apne sahaba ke liye khushi mehsoos ki, unka dukh ya jealousy kabhi nahi rakhi.

4️⃣ Cheat karne ka chance mile

👉 Agar cheating ka chance mile:
✅ Main imandari ko choose karungi, kyunki Allah sab dekh raha hai.
✅ Main short-term gain ke bajaye akhirat ko prefer karungi.
📖 Hadith: Nabi ﷺ ne farmaya: “Jo humein dhoka deta hai, wo hum mein se nahi.” (Muslim)
🌸 Nabi ﷺ ne hamesha sachai aur amanatdari ko priority di.

🌟 Discussion Prompt for GIO Session

👉 Har sister se poochhiye:
“Aapne apni zindagi mein kabhi aisi situation face ki hai?”
“Aapko sabse mushkil scenario kaunsa lagta hai?”

👉 Group Discussion: Har scenario mein aap kya karengi? Prophet ﷺ kya karte?

