“Hum sab roshni ban sakte hain – lekin roshni tabhi chalegi jab hamara akhlaq hamare ilm ke sath ho.”
👉 Pledge:

Ek bad habit chhodenge ki ,koshish karenge
Ek Sunnah shuru karenge ki ,koshish karenge
Ek dil ko narm karenge ki ,koshish karenge

Dua: Allah humari shaksiyat ko apni pasand ke mutabiq bana de. Ameen 🤲
